flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Automotive model launch announcement]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Collect model launch schedule and related data from SAP S/4HANA]
  N1 --> N2[Cortex: Cortex Auto Forecast - Predict optimal inbound logistics network design]
  N2 --> N3[Cortex: AutoML - Determine optimal outbound distribution network configuration]
  N3 --> N4[Cortex: Safety Stock Service - Develop packaging and containerization strategy]
  N4 --> N5[Cortex: RCA Service - Ensure customs and trade compliance]
  N5 --> N6{PB: CWB Lifecycle - Review and approve logistics plans}
  N6 -->|Primary| N7[PB: Remote Functions - Implement approved logistics plans and write back to SAP S/4HANA]
  N7 --> Z1[Outcome: Reduced COGS, protected service levels, accelerated time-to-market, optimized multi-echelon stock positioning, and improved OTIF.]
  N6 -->|High risk of non-compliance detected| B1[Escalate to compliance team]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Manual review and adjustment of compliance plan]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N6 -->|Significant cost savings opportunity ...| B2[Propose alternative logistics routes]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Cost optimization]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N6 -->|Unexpected disruption in logistics| B3[Activate contingency plan]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Maintain service levels and minimize delays]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]